          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Wasteful Defense Spending Reduction Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill establishes the independent Wasteful Defense Spending Reduction Commission, which shall report to Congress recommendations as to which procurement programs of the Department of Defense (DOD) should be terminated.&nbsp;DOD shall terminate a recommended program if Congress approves the termination.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-05-15T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
